
Prerequisites:

|         Arch          |   Debian/Ubuntu | macOS (Brew) |
| --------------------- | --------------- | ------------ |
| gcc                   | build-essential | gcc          |
| cmake                 | cmake           | cmake        |
| glfw-x11/glfw-wayland | libglfw3-dev    | glfw         |
| glew                  | libglew-dev     | glew         |
| glm                   | libglm-dev      | glm          |
| assimp                | libassimp-dev   | assimp       |

How to build:

mkdir build && cmake .. && make

(just `make` from later on)


How to run:
Ensure pwd is outside build, i.e. run `build/indoor`
